// Cryptol spec for `add_step` against an OPAQUE `&dyn Stepper`.
//
// We don't know what the impl of `Stepper::step` does, so the spec is
// parameterised by `step_ret` — the value the trait method happens to
// return on this call.  The SAW verification supplies `step_ret` as a
// fresh symbolic variable created inside the stub's assumed spec; the
// verifier then proves the equation for all `step_ret`.

add_step_spec : [32] -> [32] -> [32]
add_step_spec x step_ret = x + step_ret
